---
// An editor's margin note. Hidden by default; revealed when the page is
// in "Show markup" mode (html[data-markup="on"]). Renders as an inline
// red-ruled note — the page's track-changes layer. See .state/design.md.
---

<span class="annot font-mono"><slot /></span>

<style>
  .annot {
    display: none;
    margin-top: 0.55rem;
    padding-left: 0.6rem;
    border-left: 2px solid var(--color-red);
    font-size: var(--text-mono-sm);
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    line-height: 1.4;
    color: var(--color-red);
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }
  :global(html[data-markup="on"]) .annot {
    display: block;
  }
</style>
